{"tid":1779881,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"一首由傘運聽到今日嘅歌","createTime":"2019-12-12T03:26:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-12T04:22:26.000Z","uid":222499,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"efcabe5d028d10527b9f31121bd2ac9b429bc1d1","tid":1779881,"uid":222499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T03:26:58.000Z","msg":"傘下奇蹟原曲係改自 Whitney Houston 嘅When You Believe, 近幾個月香港人由2百萬人遊行到區議會選舉不斷創造傳奇, 雖然離達成五大訴求嘅目標仍然遙遠, 但香港人之間嘅守望相助係有目共睹。每次聽番歌詞自己都熱淚盈眶<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望呢條唔大家一切走落去, 編織出自由希望的天空。雖然首歌比較舊, 但都真心share俾各位巴打絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n光復香港, 時代革命!<br />\n香港人, 永不放棄!<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/QRSp0IzXWrc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FQRSp0IzXWrc&d=WPWOQTheSiAT%2FB2p9vAnAIR92%2BFrphpe0A3gOlHMrp8%3D&h=0ae6edb0\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/QRSp0IzXWrc</a>"},{"pid":"2cc386c8bfffc7500a55300d73bca337df88405b","tid":1779881,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T03:33:12.000Z","msg":"如果你真係聽足咁耐<br />\n硬係覺得你係暴大人<div style=\"text-align: center;\"></div>"},{"pid":"8d023e8821e32bac80bdfb15d6b2f3453b10868c","tid":1779881,"uid":222499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2cc386c8bfffc7500a55300d73bca337df88405b","tid":1779881,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T03:33:12.000Z","msg":"如果你真係聽足咁耐<br />\n硬係覺得你係暴大人<div style=\"text-align: center;\"></div>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T03:45:13.000Z","msg":"你點知? 記得畢業嗰年正值發生雨傘運動"},{"pid":"ff03db4196a75e52e40a3244102a6b8ed72fae32","tid":1779881,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8d023e8821e32bac80bdfb15d6b2f3453b10868c","tid":1779881,"uid":222499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2cc386c8bfffc7500a55300d73bca337df88405b","tid":1779881,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T03:33: